PLOT FILE INSIDE THIS DIRECTORY:

[1] plot_algo_w.py: this file plots the w values obtained from the runs of our 5 aglorithms. 
                    The data are taken from a csv that is passed as input to this file.
                    The x-axis of this plot corresponds to the number of algorithm is used 
					while the y-axis corresponds to the w average value.


[1] plot_algo_ql.py:  this file plots the probability that a queue is at least length x, run the simulator
                      with the 5 aglorithms.
                      The data are taken from a csv that is passed as input to this file.
                      The x-axis of this plot corresponds to the tail weight  
				 	  while the y-axis corresponds to the % of we can find a tail with that length.